help me by being a kind of ambassador for me?... Great! The village is to the east of here.</field></shadow></value><next><block type="game_show_long_text" id="I8@626RcvS4~33~(sJv$"><field name="layout">DialogLayout.Bottom</field><value name="str"><shadow type="text" id="jh?ixTM/5Y(k^5]iY_7I"><field name="TEXT">Also, I'll try and help out in battle. I'll probably be useless though.</field></shadow></value><next><block type="game_show_long_text" id="h{A,h%X#%q5fE;PUqUpA"><field name="layout">DialogLayout.Bottom</field><value name="str"><shadow type="text" id="NS`@]+[U[pt=V5xBTucl"><field name="TEXT">To make up for my uselessness, I'll teach you a spell to use in battle.</field></shadow></value><next><block type="game_show_long_text" id="{!h:hthvyJJrpf9$JMMy"><field name="layout">DialogLayout.Bottom</field><value name="str"><shadow type="text" id="5H`[dB4Z|-S#$U}5%#ec"><field name="TEXT">You learned FurBall!</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="kAzs{W]GGu(fcw^2-,|P"><field name="VAR" id="3}~%FxTxW-TN3dD.2Pp5">Spell1</field><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="snK3$kl}3la#C]]CcjS%"><field name="NUM">0</field></shadow><block type="text" id="4u-xX/4]O?lxAPvY}jnZ"><field name="TEXT">FurBall</field></block></value><next><block type="variables_change" id="`MA7f[E:1MQ]wByMwPK("><field name="VAR" id="B6l%kqHPWvDrAA1.vQIY">SpellsLearnt</field><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="/`-ZL,SKVgw]i0@K`}PP"><field name="NUM">1</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="z~H|aTK2.?s54x9L0K]w"><field name="VAR" id="l0]#DcXvyn.:`sn[o)W_">mySprite6</field><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="ooLr%,MHsOY~sZ,*MG%b"><field name="NUM">0</field></shadow><block type="spritescreate" id="E*Vb$(!s;AEz7T?nlLPT"><value name="img"><shadow type="screen_image_picker" id="4z!W@KYU^U@C7n?+aP29"><field name="img">img`
